Reviews.Title: 3 days
Reviews.Author: Mark D. Stephens
Reviews.Content: That is how long it lasted before it went out. I guess you get what you pay for. Cheap cable = cheaply made cable.I bought this cable to replace a damaged one. Taking an hour to re run this cable to have it fail within 3 days is very annoying.I get to do it all over again, except this time it will be with a higher quality cable. The only good thing about this cable was the length, which was perfect for my application, everything else is crap. I'm just glad it didn't damage my camera or dvr.
